<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Learn to canni-dance. Everyone should at least know how it works and have a hotkey set up somewhere... love it or hate it, theres times it will be the difference between winning a fight and losing it. Typical set-up might be:<br>
<br>
